projects.name: PupMe
projects.fullDescription:
Having a ruff day? Know you're gonna be stressed out later? Dreading that 9am class you have? - Don't worry anymore! With PupMe you can schedule to have cute photos of your favorite dogs and cats sent directly to your phone through push notifications.
Simply open the app, turn on 'push notifications' and schedule to have dog and cat photos sent to you when you need it most.
Features include:
Unlimited notifications
Dog / Cat options
Cat facts
100% free
V1.0.0 - iOS/Android
